Ceskaz never disappoints me ! The variety of food options available is fantastic, catering to different tastes and preferences. Each dish I tried was not only delicious but also very reasonably priced, making it a great value for money.

The breakfast options, in particular, are worth highlighting. I would highly recommend giving them a try!

The customer service deserves a special mention. The staff were attentive, friendly, and ensured a smooth dining experience.

This is definitely a place Iâ€™d revisit and recommend to anyone looking for tasty food, great service, and affordable prices in Margao.

Great place to hang out with friends, chill after a hard day or even grab an exotic break.  The variety,  flavors and plating makes you enjoy every bite!

Come as a group and order variety so you can taste different stuff!

Very cozy cafe. The ambiance is great too. Service is super fast. We were attended by a very sweet lady. Ordered their roast chicken crossiant, turkish adana chicken kebab roll, caramel cappuccino and hazelnut cappuccino. The chicken crossiant came loadded with chicken along with tomato, olives, and lettuce and sauces. The kebab roll was mouthwatering, juicy loaded with pickled onions and spices. And the cappuccinos were a warm hug in the winters. Food was on point. Tried their chocolate and fruit tart as well which was so heavenly. Definitely worth another visit. Highly recommended
